# No leftover old-brand strings

When performing a rebrand, ensure there are **zero** leftover mentions of the previous brand.

## Requirements
- Search for the old brand name and replace/update all occurrences.
- Also check for common “near matches”:
  - old support emails/domains (e.g. `@oldbrand.com`)
  - product names, testimonials, footer blurb
  - document title/favicon alt text

## Repo references (examples)
- Document title + favicon: `index.html`
- Central copy/data: `src/constants/index.js`
- Common sections with brand mentions: `src/sections/Hero.jsx`, `src/sections/Footer.jsx`

## Reporting
In the summary, include a short **Leftovers check** section:
- old-brand search terms used
- files changed (high-level)
- any intentional exceptions (rare; must be explicit)
